name: Vessels 142: MANDRAKE THE SEEKER
description: The life of a seeker is a hard and lonely one. Forever out on your own, forging ahead of the rest of the hunting party, scrabbling around in the dirt looking for tracks and clues, with only your wits and your giant novelty magnifying glass for company. It’s all made worthwhile, however, when you catch your first glimpse of some proud and magnificent alien creature, never-before-seen by human eyes, and know that you’re about to help the rest of your hunting party sneak up on it and shoot it in the back.
